what's in it for me

prod Wino Willy

lyrics.text:
You know this talk is not cheap I'm at Boa puttin up bands every week 
They like me cuz I'm low key 
Out in public she chill but at home she a freak 
All of my garments unique thrift God still in this bitch and my bag is antique 
Im not addressing no tweet if it's not to my face you not talking to me 

I got a play every day of the week
Everyone betting on me and my team
Wood Grain interior Creme on the seats 
Might go to Papis for sumn to eat

Silk on the fleece
Silk on the sheet
Cashmere devut 
Elegant when I sleep 
Treat a work trip 
Like vacation at peace 
Now that I'm winning they all wanna piece
You gotta tell me what's in it for me
Everything ain't gone align with my chi

If I say no will you be mad at me 
I don't like when you entitled to me 
I had to earn everything that you see 
Strength in my words so I watch how I speak 
Gas and my tank and my pack never cheap 
My aura strong it's not made for the weak


This is not new to me 
Lately be working like theres about 3 of me 
I came from poverty I deserve luxury
If I look out for you will go up for me 
You gotta tell me Whats in it for me 
They think it's selfish but whole life been selfless and I now that I put myself first they get jealous
If you can't do me like I do me it's pointless
We all a reflection 
And when love me my surroundings reflect it 
I don't call it hate 
I just call it projections 
We can't elevate if we put here finesse each other 
Please show me what's real 

Tell me the truth and we might have a deal 
Please be authentic and fuck how they feel 
Manifest worth and remember freewill 
Free all my bruddas up out that box l
I got some ppl still sleeping on cots 
That's why I get it for me and the gang 
When they let them boys out we gone sleep on a Yacht 
Playing for keeps I created my spot 

It was the best of times
It was the worst of times 
But we still made the time to be on time for our blessings 
Gratitude in ever direction
